				<PARA style-name="EdNoteSm" style-name-escaped="EdNoteSm" style-id="0-0-0-20">
					<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Editor&apos;s note:</CHARFORMAT> former Chapter 8, relating to Transportation benefits, was renumbered as <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T06C007SC" destination-id="0-0-0-15193">6 RCNY Chapter 7, Subchapter C</LINK>. See City Record 8/21/2018, eff. 9/20/2018. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
