							<RECORD id="0-0-0-20714" number="24252" version="2170">
								<HEADING>§ 8-01 Biometric Identifier Information Signage.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17408" name="T06C008_8-01"/>§ 8-01 Biometric Identifier Information Signage.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131491" number="24253" version="2497">
									<PARA>To comply with § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="22-1202" destination-id="0-0-0-0">22-1202</LINK> of <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T22C012" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 12 of Title 22</LINK> of the New York City Administrative Code, a commercial establishment covered by such section must post a sign in a clear and conspicuous manner at every entrance used by customers in a size of at least 8.5 inches by 11 inches that discloses if customers&apos; biometric identifier information is being collected, retained, converted, stored, or shared. The requirements of this section may be fulfilled by posting a color copy of the Biometric Identifier Information Disclosure, as made publicly available on the Department&apos;s website, in a clear and conspicuous manner at every entrance used by customers in a size of at least 8.5 inches by 11 inches.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131490" number="24254" version="2948">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/16/2021, eff. 1/15/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
